WEBVTT

01:32.120 --> 01:34.950
[How dare you!?]

01:35.020 --> 01:37.900
[Episode 7]

01:45.200 --> 01:48.530
The plan was to get Xie Yong'er
to spill the truth when drunk,

01:49.640 --> 01:52.100
but I ended up
revealing everything myself.

02:03.500 --> 02:05.300
I thought I held the script,

02:06.920 --> 02:09.430
but Prince Duan
was the one truly above all.

02:13.680 --> 02:16.430
I even revealed my only way to survive.

02:18.680 --> 02:19.240
I...

02:21.400 --> 02:23.310
must be doomed now.

02:28.910 --> 02:29.560
My Lady,

02:29.840 --> 02:31.370
it's time to wash and dress.

02:35.750 --> 02:37.530
My Lady, you've been drinking?

02:38.910 --> 02:39.440
Be quiet.

02:40.470 --> 02:41.270
My head hurts.

02:41.910 --> 02:43.310
Let me sleep a bit longer.

02:44.150 --> 02:45.120
That won't do.

02:45.750 --> 02:47.520
You are to pay your respects
to the Empress Dowager today.

02:47.520 --> 02:49.360
Why do I have to see her again?

02:52.310 --> 02:54.640
Nothing good ever comes from meeting her.

02:55.170 --> 02:56.590
Can't I just pretend to be sick?

02:56.590 --> 03:00.120
His Majesty just promoted
Concubine Xie to Consort this morning.

03:00.120 --> 03:03.120
If you don't attend,
you'll face even more criticism.

03:03.870 --> 03:06.400
The Emperor's heart
is truly unpredictable.

03:07.310 --> 03:09.120
Greetings, Your Majesty

03:09.280 --> 03:11.080
Greetings,
Your Majesty the Empress Dowager.

03:11.080 --> 03:12.400
May Your Majesty
be blessed with good fortune.

03:12.400 --> 03:14.310
May Your Majesty the
Empress Dowager enjoy peace and health.

03:14.310 --> 03:15.040
You may rise.

03:15.630 --> 03:17.230
Everyone, please be seated.

03:17.560 --> 03:18.890
Thank you, Your Majesty

03:18.910 --> 03:20.110
and Empress Dowager.

03:26.240 --> 03:28.079
A hangover is truly miserable.

03:51.240 --> 03:51.970
Consort Xie.

03:53.310 --> 03:54.170
Come to my side.

04:09.430 --> 04:10.230
Your Majesty.

04:13.150 --> 04:13.950
So beautiful.

04:16.560 --> 04:17.120
Emperor,

04:18.680 --> 04:20.310
the Flower Festival Banquet
is approaching.

04:20.310 --> 04:21.510
What are your plans?

04:25.430 --> 04:26.240
Your Majesty,

04:26.750 --> 04:29.000
with the Flower Festival Banquet
drawing near and flowers in full bloom,

04:29.000 --> 04:30.190
our Great Xia now

04:30.270 --> 04:32.240
enjoys peace and prosperity.

04:32.870 --> 04:34.680
Therefore, I believe

04:34.950 --> 04:36.190
all of us consorts

04:36.270 --> 04:37.870
should each contribute our strengths

04:37.870 --> 04:39.870
and do our part
to sing the praises of the nation.

04:39.870 --> 04:40.470
Am I right?

04:40.750 --> 04:41.550
That's right.

04:41.920 --> 04:44.390
I personally picked 100 kinds of flowers

04:44.750 --> 04:46.720
and made them into Hundred Flower Cakes.

04:46.720 --> 04:47.320
They taste

04:47.630 --> 04:48.560
excellent.

04:48.630 --> 04:50.690
I've been preparing since last year.

04:50.870 --> 04:54.750
I'm embroidering an 8-foot-long piece
called Blossoms and Wealth.

04:55.159 --> 04:56.600
By the time
of the Flower Festival Banquet,

04:56.600 --> 04:57.730
it will be finished.

04:58.720 --> 05:00.300
After years of study,

05:00.560 --> 05:02.510
I finally cultivated a new flower species.

05:02.510 --> 05:04.710
Putting so much thought into one thing?

05:04.920 --> 05:06.430
Yet they seem to enjoy it.

05:06.920 --> 05:07.980
Come to think of it,

05:08.160 --> 05:09.720
being just a simple 2D character

05:09.720 --> 05:11.190
seems quite happy at least.

05:11.190 --> 05:12.480
But the more I know,

05:12.830 --> 05:14.160
the more worries I have.

05:14.240 --> 05:15.970
You've all put in great effort.

05:16.160 --> 05:18.100
I am very pleased.

05:19.600 --> 05:20.130
Emperor,

05:21.190 --> 05:22.190
what do you think?

05:22.480 --> 05:23.830
Which do you prefer?

05:34.390 --> 05:35.159
Last night,

05:35.950 --> 05:38.550
the dances
Consort Xie performed in my chamber

05:39.190 --> 05:40.520
were quite impressive.

05:40.560 --> 05:41.909
I danced?

05:42.390 --> 05:43.990
I don't remember that at all!

05:44.560 --> 05:45.420
At the banquet,

05:46.600 --> 05:48.800
let's have Consort Xie perform a dance.

05:49.070 --> 05:49.870
Your Majesty...

05:49.870 --> 05:50.670
It's settled.

05:52.040 --> 05:52.900
Your Highness,

05:53.040 --> 05:54.370
are you feeling unwell?

06:03.920 --> 06:05.850
I've caught a slight cold recently

06:06.480 --> 06:07.480
and feel a bit off.

06:08.680 --> 06:09.920
On such a fine day,

06:11.440 --> 06:13.240
I'd better excuse myself

06:13.960 --> 06:16.870
so as not to spoil Your Majesty's and
the Empress Dowager's enjoyment.

06:16.870 --> 06:18.800
What a pitiful look.

06:18.870 --> 06:19.750
How scheming.

06:19.770 --> 06:21.600
Stop pretending, Sister.

06:21.680 --> 06:23.680
Pretending to be sick for sympathy?

06:24.000 --> 06:25.000
I hope His Majesty

06:25.000 --> 06:27.160
doesn't fall for this
"white lotus"'s trick.

06:27.160 --> 06:29.000
Well, Consort Yu's heal—

06:29.040 --> 06:29.570
Get lost.

06:38.159 --> 06:39.159
What a shame.

06:39.409 --> 06:40.830
She was trying to act pitiful,

06:40.830 --> 06:42.490
but turned out truly pitiful.

06:42.600 --> 06:44.040
His Majesty is sick of her now.

06:44.040 --> 06:45.040
Serves her right.

06:48.159 --> 06:48.710
My dear,

06:50.100 --> 06:51.960
come to my chamber again tonight,

06:52.800 --> 06:53.330
alright?

07:06.050 --> 07:08.240
Isn't that Noble Consort Yu
who just lost favor?

07:08.240 --> 07:09.160
Stop looking.

07:10.600 --> 07:13.240
Xiahou Dan's performance
of favoring the new over the old

07:13.240 --> 07:14.510
is quite convincing.

07:15.680 --> 07:17.240
According to the original story,

07:17.240 --> 07:19.480
by now, I, the demonic consort,
should have been

07:19.480 --> 07:21.360
completely suppressed by Xie Yong'er,

07:21.360 --> 07:23.560
never able to turn things around again.

07:24.040 --> 07:25.170
Turn things around?

07:25.360 --> 07:27.020
Whether it's me, Xie Yong'er,

07:27.040 --> 07:28.100
or even Xiahou Dan—

07:28.560 --> 07:31.690
we might all just be 2D characters
in Prince Duan's eyes.

07:39.240 --> 07:39.700
My Lady.

07:47.740 --> 07:51.980
[Let's have a chat
in the flower house at midnight]

07:56.150 --> 07:57.810
What's meant to come has come.

08:29.430 --> 08:29.990
Wanyin.

08:32.110 --> 08:32.700
I'm here.

08:37.150 --> 08:38.000
Come to me.

08:40.720 --> 08:41.510
This man

08:43.549 --> 08:44.720
is so good at this.

08:50.000 --> 08:50.860
I was careless.

08:51.560 --> 08:54.760
I should have brought Mr. Bei
or secret guards for safety.

08:55.120 --> 08:55.960
But he probably won't

08:55.960 --> 08:57.420
take my life at this stage.

08:58.510 --> 08:59.910
I'll struggle a bit first

09:00.720 --> 09:01.150
to see

09:01.840 --> 09:03.300
what level he's really at.

09:06.120 --> 09:07.650
Your Highness, what did you

09:07.670 --> 09:08.630
ask me here for?

09:09.270 --> 09:10.310
Earlier today,

09:10.790 --> 09:12.050
I visited Minister Yu.

09:13.030 --> 09:14.270
He misses you

09:15.440 --> 09:18.100
and wants to know
how you're doing in the palace.

09:18.170 --> 09:19.200
So I thought

09:20.120 --> 09:21.320
I'd ask on his behalf.

09:22.200 --> 09:24.800
That's very thoughtful of you,
Your Highness.

09:25.270 --> 09:26.060
However...

09:28.440 --> 09:29.750
life in the palace...

09:30.840 --> 09:31.840
is just like this.

09:34.840 --> 09:37.240
Wanyin, do you have something
on your mind?

09:42.630 --> 09:43.530
Concubine Xie

09:44.750 --> 09:46.610
attended His Majesty last night.

09:47.390 --> 09:48.190
This morning,

09:48.550 --> 09:50.150
she was promoted to Consort.

09:51.560 --> 09:52.540
Your Highness,

09:53.510 --> 09:55.310
what do you think of Consort Xie?

09:59.030 --> 10:00.560
She is His Majesty's woman.

10:01.360 --> 10:02.420
I dare not comment.

10:02.480 --> 10:03.280
What about me?

10:04.080 --> 10:05.080
Your Highness,

10:05.390 --> 10:06.650
what do you think of me?

10:07.120 --> 10:08.920
Like viewing a flower through the mist,

10:08.920 --> 10:10.250
I can't see you clearly.

10:10.480 --> 10:11.600
Your Highness,

10:12.000 --> 10:13.330
why do you feel this way?

10:14.120 --> 10:14.630
Wanyin,

10:16.030 --> 10:17.960
we've known each other
for quite some time.

10:17.960 --> 10:19.290
Perhaps some things...

10:20.240 --> 10:21.900
should be spoken plainly now.

10:25.000 --> 10:25.730
For example?

10:26.270 --> 10:27.130
For example...

10:30.030 --> 10:30.670
who...

10:33.320 --> 10:35.120
are you exactly?

10:39.710 --> 10:40.140
I...

10:41.200 --> 10:42.080
Or...

10:42.960 --> 10:44.080
who is His Majesty?

10:45.360 --> 10:47.480
And who is Xie Yong'er?

10:52.400 --> 10:54.060
The worst guess has come true.

10:55.360 --> 10:56.890
He saw through Xie Yong'er,

10:57.600 --> 10:59.120
perhaps because this lovesick fool

10:59.120 --> 11:00.250
let something slip.

11:01.390 --> 11:02.990
That he can see through me too

11:03.600 --> 11:05.860
might be because I slipped up somewhere.

11:06.720 --> 11:07.980
But he even saw through Xiahou Dan,

11:07.980 --> 11:09.030
that master actor.

11:09.030 --> 11:10.160
That's impossible.

11:10.870 --> 11:11.530
Which means

11:12.550 --> 11:13.480
he can only be

11:15.150 --> 11:16.680
standing on a higher level.

11:23.160 --> 11:25.420
Wanyin, there's no need to be so nervous.

11:26.980 --> 11:28.780
I have never meant you any harm.

11:29.550 --> 11:31.680
And since you can foresee some things,

11:31.870 --> 11:33.670
you should know that choosing me

11:34.360 --> 11:36.320
is the wiser choice.

11:38.400 --> 11:40.000
Since you already know everything,

11:40.000 --> 11:41.260
what do you need me for?

11:41.270 --> 11:43.670
I didn't come to you
to have you do anything.

11:45.750 --> 11:47.910
I came because I've fallen for you.

11:50.600 --> 11:52.400
We're not even the same species.

11:53.750 --> 11:55.080
Not even from the same dimension.

11:55.080 --> 11:56.480
How could you fall for me?

12:03.960 --> 12:04.420
Well...

12:06.550 --> 12:08.610
That doesn't seem to matter, does it?

12:10.630 --> 12:11.080
So

12:14.070 --> 12:15.620
you like me as a character?

12:18.630 --> 12:20.030
Otherwise, why would I

12:20.670 --> 12:22.400
have chosen you from the start?

12:24.630 --> 12:26.150
Then when we first met,

12:26.910 --> 12:27.720
why didn't you say it outright?

12:27.720 --> 12:28.270
Wanyin,

12:28.550 --> 12:30.610
I'll tell you some things gradually.

12:31.480 --> 12:33.480
All you need to do is think carefully

12:33.720 --> 12:35.720
about whose side you should stand on

12:36.480 --> 12:38.150
to make the wisest choice.

12:45.620 --> 12:48.130
[Your Majesty,]

12:48.130 --> 12:50.650
[please eliminate the demonic consort
to strengthen the court]

13:02.960 --> 13:05.160
Consort Yu went to the Imperial Garden.

13:05.510 --> 13:08.030
She's having
a secret meeting with Prince Duan.

13:08.030 --> 13:08.440
Dan,

13:09.360 --> 13:10.560
what are your orders?

13:11.600 --> 13:12.240
No orders.

13:13.960 --> 13:14.820
Don't you care?

13:17.360 --> 13:18.750
I know you like her.

13:19.790 --> 13:21.360
But she shares a bed with you.

13:21.360 --> 13:24.220
If she turns against you,
it would be too dangerous.

13:26.440 --> 13:28.170
Have you ever considered that,

13:29.210 --> 13:30.470
from her perspective,

13:32.470 --> 13:34.840
[Your Majesty,
why haven't you taken action yet?]

13:32.720 --> 13:33.630
Prince Duan

13:34.860 --> 13:36.940
[Don't let impulsiveness
ruin a good opportunity]

13:35.870 --> 13:37.270
is indeed a safer option?

13:37.510 --> 13:38.120
Why?

13:38.850 --> 13:39.510
Haven't you already known

13:39.510 --> 13:41.030
Prince Duan's plan?

13:42.440 --> 13:44.170
Knowing it and being confident

13:45.480 --> 13:46.940
are two different things.

13:49.320 --> 13:50.520
She wants to survive,

13:51.620 --> 13:53.020
and that's only natural.

13:53.380 --> 13:54.210
♪ Tell me ♪

13:54.920 --> 13:58.330
♪ Why so many laments echo in the wind ♪

13:55.510 --> 13:55.960
Dan,

13:58.330 --> 14:00.010
is she really that important?

14:00.060 --> 14:01.120
♪ Walk past me ♪

14:01.520 --> 14:05.090
♪ Like an aloof passerby ♪

14:01.600 --> 14:03.080
You shouldn't let love

14:03.630 --> 14:04.830
cloud your judgment.

14:06.460 --> 14:08.940
♪ Don't watch me as the rain falls ♪

14:08.200 --> 14:09.360
She is my lifeline.

14:09.780 --> 14:12.560
♪ Love burns too hot as it passes ♪

14:12.770 --> 14:14.150
What about Xiahou Dan?

14:13.290 --> 14:19.040
♪ Even a lifetime of war
cannot be extinguished ♪

14:14.610 --> 14:15.780
He won't.

14:16.600 --> 14:17.030
Why?

14:17.550 --> 14:18.120
Even I

14:19.440 --> 14:21.180
have been hesitating over

14:20.230 --> 14:21.260
♪ Blame me ♪

14:21.950 --> 14:25.430
♪ For the frailty of fate ♪

14:23.720 --> 14:25.610
whether to ally with him.

14:27.050 --> 14:28.130
♪ Hide me ♪

14:27.530 --> 14:28.310
Yet he

14:28.550 --> 14:32.600
♪ With light snow or thick ink ♪

14:30.130 --> 14:31.670
has always chosen me

14:33.900 --> 14:36.280
♪ We met in the crowd ♪

14:34.080 --> 14:35.270
without wavering.

14:37.200 --> 14:39.790
♪ There's no mistake in this life ♪

14:40.700 --> 14:43.620
♪ I only regret being clumsy in words ♪

14:41.000 --> 14:42.320
You are the bravest

14:43.680 --> 14:45.840
♪ And shrinking from speaking it out ♪

14:45.550 --> 14:47.030
and most formidable person

14:46.240 --> 14:48.690
♪ Even when destiny mocked me, hurt me ♪

14:48.600 --> 14:49.600
I've seen in my two lives.

14:48.740 --> 14:50.500
♪ Destroyed me, or trapped me ♪

14:50.530 --> 14:53.050
♪ I never yielded ♪

14:52.030 --> 14:53.360
You'll definitely have the last laugh,

14:53.360 --> 14:54.850
♪ But why ♪

14:55.090 --> 14:59.670
♪ Can't I bear to see
even a single tear in your eyes? ♪

14:55.440 --> 14:56.440
fighting your way

14:57.720 --> 14:59.000
to a bright new world.

14:59.990 --> 15:02.310
♪ But we once fell in love, went wild ♪

15:02.360 --> 15:03.080
So,

15:02.400 --> 15:04.250
♪ Split up, and lost each other ♪

15:04.280 --> 15:06.600
♪ They are
all unforgettable memories to me ♪

15:05.160 --> 15:07.100
whatever decision she makes,
I will support it,

15:07.020 --> 15:08.750
♪ The first time I met you ♪

15:09.150 --> 15:09.750
including...

15:09.150 --> 15:16.970
♪ It felt like something suddenly
lit up my soul ♪

15:14.670 --> 15:15.330
leaving me.

15:30.000 --> 15:31.000
I'm done playing.

15:31.670 --> 15:33.070
How can we even continue?

15:41.790 --> 15:42.720
I was thinking

15:43.240 --> 15:45.480
the four of us
could play mahjong together.

15:45.480 --> 15:47.200
Instead, he drew
a heavenly hand right off the deal

15:47.200 --> 15:48.530
and beat all three of us.

15:49.240 --> 15:50.550
Fallen for me?

15:52.320 --> 15:53.980
You'd fall for a 2D character?

15:56.150 --> 15:56.930
Yeah right.

15:59.240 --> 16:00.110
Wanyin.

16:01.550 --> 16:02.080
Mr. Bei?

16:03.030 --> 16:04.560
You were late getting back,

16:04.670 --> 16:06.930
so I prepared some tea and snacks for you.

16:07.200 --> 16:08.660
Don't forget to have them.

16:10.840 --> 16:11.410
Okay.

16:11.750 --> 16:12.810
Thank you, Mr. Bei.

16:13.000 --> 16:14.330
Get some rest early too.

16:20.960 --> 16:22.490
Mr. Bei is really good to me.

16:23.870 --> 16:25.510
Should I tell him

16:26.000 --> 16:27.730
and CEO Dan what just happened?

16:30.840 --> 16:31.440
Forget it.

16:32.670 --> 16:34.070
Better they know nothing

16:35.080 --> 16:37.080
than for us all to be upset together.

16:52.630 --> 16:53.480
I wonder

16:54.510 --> 16:56.770
what my name
is in this book I'm living in,

16:57.840 --> 16:59.440
and how many pages I'll last.

17:03.150 --> 17:03.910
Maybe

17:04.510 --> 17:05.550
Xu Yao's death

17:06.550 --> 17:08.310
is also part of the plot.

17:16.200 --> 17:17.599
What's the point of this?

17:19.440 --> 17:19.880
Yeah.

17:22.160 --> 17:23.480
What's the point?

17:28.000 --> 17:28.540
[Turning the Deputy Minister of Revenue
to our side—failed]

17:28.560 --> 17:29.250
[Spreading false information—failed]

17:29.680 --> 17:30.210
[Kill the imperial censor's
secret guards in the backyard]

17:30.210 --> 17:30.740
[to eliminate future threats.]

17:37.160 --> 17:37.680
Mr. Bei!

17:38.920 --> 17:39.780
Consort Xie,

17:40.110 --> 17:40.840
you're here.

17:41.400 --> 17:42.000
Eunuch An.

17:43.200 --> 17:44.060
Your Highness!

17:44.200 --> 17:46.960
Our Consort has an urgent matter
to discuss with His Majesty.

17:46.960 --> 17:48.360
No one is to disturb them.

17:49.430 --> 17:50.510
Well... yes.

17:51.070 --> 17:55.790
[Yongyan Hall]

17:59.880 --> 18:01.360
Your Highness, well...

18:01.790 --> 18:03.720
Perhaps you should return for now.

18:08.200 --> 18:08.660
CEO Dan!

18:09.240 --> 18:09.700
CEO Dan!

18:10.830 --> 18:11.760
Why are you here?

18:12.720 --> 18:14.310
There really is something wrong
with Prince Duan.

18:14.310 --> 18:15.370
Why do you say that?

18:15.820 --> 18:16.760
Xu Yao's book

18:17.110 --> 18:18.970
records his plans in such detail.

18:19.350 --> 18:20.270
If Xiahou Bo

18:20.270 --> 18:22.200
really stands at the highest level,

18:22.200 --> 18:24.730
how could this book
have ended up in our hands?

18:25.000 --> 18:27.060
Assuming he let us find it on purpose,

18:27.100 --> 18:28.960
what benefit would that be to him?

18:29.440 --> 18:31.640
The easiest way to defeat you

18:31.800 --> 18:34.130
is to keep us in the dark
about everything.

18:34.400 --> 18:34.730
Also,

18:35.400 --> 18:36.880
if he knew I was a transmigrator,

18:36.880 --> 18:38.480
why didn't he ask me directly?

18:38.480 --> 18:40.340
Why keep testing me over and over?

18:40.830 --> 18:42.160
And I met with him today.

18:43.030 --> 18:44.750
When I said
we're not even the same species,

18:44.750 --> 18:46.610
not even from the same dimension,

18:46.750 --> 18:48.160
he clearly hesitated.

18:48.750 --> 18:50.080
What does that suggest?

18:50.110 --> 18:51.200
It suggests...

18:52.270 --> 18:54.400
that his show of initiative

18:55.160 --> 18:57.160
may simply be because he discovered

18:57.920 --> 18:59.860
our abnormality in some way?

19:00.920 --> 19:01.960
In his eyes,

19:02.570 --> 19:04.060
we might be the kind of

19:04.440 --> 19:05.540
semi-divine beings with foresight

19:05.540 --> 19:07.070
who can foresee the future.

19:08.260 --> 19:10.720
And he thinks
the three of us are the same kind.

19:10.720 --> 19:11.790
You, me,

19:12.480 --> 19:13.410
and Xie Yong'er?

19:14.160 --> 19:14.720
So

19:15.160 --> 19:16.630
if he doesn't trust Xie Yong'er,

19:16.630 --> 19:18.360
he won't trust you or me either.

19:19.550 --> 19:20.470
So...

19:20.920 --> 19:22.650
he's still just a 2D character?

19:24.750 --> 19:25.880
I need to find a way

19:26.200 --> 19:27.530
to test him thoroughly.

19:28.530 --> 19:29.130
By the way,

19:29.310 --> 19:30.070
shouldn't we

19:30.160 --> 19:32.020
hurry up and find those scholars?

19:34.400 --> 19:35.600
Why are you laughing?

19:35.920 --> 19:37.310
You told me about

19:38.110 --> 19:39.770
your private meeting with him
just like that?

19:39.770 --> 19:41.640
I told you so many important things,

19:41.640 --> 19:42.920
and that's your focus?

19:43.030 --> 19:44.160
I heard everything.

19:45.920 --> 19:47.920
But I think what's more important is

19:50.740 --> 19:52.470
whether we should have hot pot.

20:00.680 --> 20:02.270
Alright, alright. My bad, my bad.

20:02.270 --> 20:02.940
Let's go.

20:03.000 --> 20:03.590
Let's eat hot pot.

20:03.590 --> 20:04.120
Let's go.

20:20.200 --> 20:21.400
Why isn't he here yet?

20:22.830 --> 20:24.290
He didn't back out, did he?

20:26.720 --> 20:27.960
Have you memorized

20:28.240 --> 20:29.350
the scholars' names and traits?

20:29.350 --> 20:30.110
This battle

20:30.110 --> 20:32.510
will decide the fate
of our Fishball Squad.

20:34.400 --> 20:35.200
Don't worry.

20:35.880 --> 20:36.680
Piece of cake.

20:39.540 --> 20:41.200
I've got it all under control.

20:41.550 --> 20:43.210
So how did you get them to come?

20:51.480 --> 20:52.510
Buns!

20:52.510 --> 20:54.420
Hot, delicious buns!

20:55.270 --> 20:56.530
Please keep it.

20:58.160 --> 21:00.240
The realm
has fallen into the hands of traitors.

21:00.240 --> 21:02.440
We're at a critical moment of survival.

21:03.000 --> 21:04.460
The people are exhausted,

21:04.550 --> 21:06.080
resources are running dry,

21:06.270 --> 21:07.930
the soldiers are growing old,

21:08.030 --> 21:10.430
and the people's hearts are drifting away.

21:11.680 --> 21:13.030
To make peace with a life

21:13.960 --> 21:15.560
of frustrated aspirations;

21:15.680 --> 21:17.280
steeds and spears were never

21:18.200 --> 21:19.240
my desire.

21:21.400 --> 21:22.830
Sir, excellent poem!

21:23.270 --> 21:24.170
I have one too.

21:24.350 --> 21:25.410
Please take a look.

21:27.270 --> 21:28.680
A true gentleman seizes the moment,

21:28.680 --> 21:30.240
and a wise man understands his fate.

21:30.240 --> 21:31.070
Though old,

21:31.550 --> 21:33.400
one's resolve need not fade;

21:34.640 --> 21:36.160
though poor, one's ambition

21:36.160 --> 21:37.400
should not fall.

21:38.310 --> 21:39.920
Loyal and righteous men
have all but perished,

21:39.240 --> 21:41.420
[Discourses on Salt and Iron]

21:40.720 --> 21:43.980
while troubles within and without
rise one after another.

21:45.350 --> 21:46.030
Fellow scholars,

21:45.880 --> 21:47.630
[Du Shan]

21:46.310 --> 21:48.270
you have studied diligently for decades,

21:48.270 --> 21:49.440
upholding righteousness
with quiet forbearance amid chaos.

21:49.440 --> 21:50.070
-Don't rush.
-Thank you.

21:50.070 --> 21:52.270
You possess extraordinary integrity.

21:53.830 --> 21:55.430
The rise and fall of the realm

21:55.510 --> 21:56.640
concerns every man.

21:58.680 --> 21:59.880
When the land is adrift,

21:59.880 --> 22:01.310
rather than replacing the ruler,

22:01.310 --> 22:03.590
it's better to destroy the old rules
and rebuild.

22:03.590 --> 22:05.070
I wish to befriend all you heroes

22:05.070 --> 22:06.270
and shape the nation,

22:06.710 --> 22:08.240
saving the collapsing tide

22:08.350 --> 22:10.410
and supporting the falling edifice.

22:13.460 --> 22:15.240
Let's set the heart for Heaven and Earth,

22:15.240 --> 22:16.770
secure life for the people,

22:16.950 --> 22:19.110
carry on the lost teachings of the sages,

22:19.110 --> 22:21.840
and bring lasting peace
for generations to come.

22:23.200 --> 22:25.800
Let's gather
at East Lake at the end of the month

22:26.240 --> 22:27.680
to discuss our grand plan.

22:27.680 --> 22:29.410
This journey may be dangerous.

22:29.830 --> 22:30.560
I ask that you

22:31.240 --> 22:32.370
travel with caution

22:33.270 --> 22:34.530
to ensure your safety.

22:37.590 --> 22:39.790
As a CEO, he really deserves your title.

22:40.550 --> 22:41.680
His literary talent

22:41.960 --> 22:43.490
puts me, a corporate drone,

22:43.750 --> 22:45.550
to shame. I can't compare at all.

22:58.400 --> 22:58.830
Cen.

23:00.160 --> 23:01.220
Let me borrow this.

23:10.960 --> 23:12.640
We came to answer your invitation

23:12.640 --> 23:14.920
because we were moved
by the words in your letter

23:14.920 --> 23:16.680
and wished to meet a kindred spirit.

23:16.680 --> 23:17.310
Yet today,

23:17.590 --> 23:20.390
all you've arranged
is drinking and sightseeing.

23:20.480 --> 23:21.740
This hardly feels like

23:21.790 --> 23:24.520
the long-awaited meeting
your letter promised.

23:26.160 --> 23:27.480
You have all traveled far,

23:27.480 --> 23:29.940
and endured the discomfort
of being veiled.

23:30.400 --> 23:30.880
I

23:31.310 --> 23:32.840
truly feel uneasy about it.

23:33.550 --> 23:34.550
As my letter said,

23:35.030 --> 23:36.890
I have long admired your talents.

23:37.510 --> 23:39.240
The brilliant essays you have written,

23:39.240 --> 23:42.030
I often read aloud to myself
and ponder in my heart.

23:42.030 --> 23:42.550
When I close the book...

23:42.550 --> 23:43.350
Let's skip

23:43.680 --> 23:44.740
the pleasantries.

23:51.750 --> 23:53.400
Establishing offices
and building the nation

23:53.400 --> 23:55.880
is meant to provide the people
with the means to live;

23:55.880 --> 23:57.550
levying taxes and collecting revenue

23:57.550 --> 23:59.030
is to support the state.

24:00.030 --> 24:01.000
All taxation

24:01.790 --> 24:02.240
must

24:03.240 --> 24:04.840
consider people's strength

24:05.240 --> 24:06.840
and the land's suitability.

24:08.590 --> 24:09.650
This is Li's essay?

24:09.920 --> 24:11.180
Li Yunxi from Zhuozhou

24:11.920 --> 24:13.380
is erudite and ambitious,

24:13.550 --> 24:14.640
of noble character,

24:14.640 --> 24:15.960
upright and unyielding,

24:15.960 --> 24:17.160
frank and outspoken.

24:17.640 --> 24:19.000
If he heads the Ministry of Revenue,

24:19.000 --> 24:21.170
his meticulous nature

24:21.590 --> 24:23.520
will surely deter all corruption.

24:24.640 --> 24:25.770
I must drink to that.

24:30.640 --> 24:31.350
You've certainly

24:31.350 --> 24:32.480
done your homework.

24:35.790 --> 24:37.050
Du Shan from Bingzhou,

24:37.160 --> 24:38.620
with his piece "Red Kite,"

24:38.680 --> 24:39.610
moved the world.

24:40.030 --> 24:41.680
If he heads the Ministry of Rites,

24:41.680 --> 24:44.280
he will bring honor
and integrity to Great Xia.

24:45.360 --> 24:46.960
I don't deserve such praise.

24:47.790 --> 24:49.320
The key to river management

24:49.640 --> 24:51.340
is first to understand its principles,

24:51.340 --> 24:52.920
then adapt to circumstances,

24:52.920 --> 24:54.590
and weigh with human compassion.

24:54.590 --> 24:56.120
Er Lan's "River Transport"

24:56.350 --> 24:58.510
is insightful yet accessible,

24:59.480 --> 25:00.440
every word a gem.

25:01.160 --> 25:02.430
If he heads the Ministry of Works,

25:02.430 --> 25:04.350
the population growth of Great Xia

25:04.350 --> 25:05.550
will be within reach.

25:07.500 --> 25:09.100
Yang is clever and flexible,

25:09.200 --> 25:10.550
skilled in mathematics.

25:10.550 --> 25:11.830
Now that times have changed,

25:11.830 --> 25:13.100
today, the Ministry of Personnel

25:13.100 --> 25:14.570
needs someone like you

25:14.930 --> 25:16.590
to choose talent

25:16.790 --> 25:18.160
without prejudice.

25:18.510 --> 25:19.570
I'll drink to that.

25:21.550 --> 25:22.200
Wang Zhao

25:23.110 --> 25:24.880
is honest and straightforward,

25:24.880 --> 25:25.740
a pleasure

25:26.070 --> 25:27.260
to meet.

25:28.160 --> 25:30.680
In the future, he may well serve
in the State Ceremonial Bureau,

25:30.680 --> 25:32.280
mediating between nations.

25:33.880 --> 25:34.720
You

25:35.330 --> 25:37.660
promised everyone such grand prospects.

25:39.680 --> 25:40.240
So,

25:40.750 --> 25:42.080
what role am I to take on?

25:42.310 --> 25:43.960
Food is the first necessity of the people.

25:43.960 --> 25:45.920
Cen, if you serve
as an agricultural official,

25:45.920 --> 25:47.780
it will be a great blessing to all.

25:47.790 --> 25:48.590
The northwest now

25:48.590 --> 25:49.920
suffers from severe drought,

25:49.920 --> 25:51.310
while the southwest is plagued by floods.

25:51.310 --> 25:51.920
Recently,

25:52.200 --> 25:54.340
I came across a book
from the Western Regions

25:54.340 --> 25:55.400
that records a crop

25:55.570 --> 25:56.770
resistant to lodging

25:56.960 --> 25:58.200
and tolerant of both drought and flooding.

25:58.200 --> 25:59.330
If there is a chance,

25:59.440 --> 26:00.890
I would like to discuss it with you

26:00.890 --> 26:01.950
through the night.

26:12.240 --> 26:12.910
Your Highness,

26:12.910 --> 26:14.210
our men just sent word.

26:14.680 --> 26:16.640
The Emperor has secretly left the palace
and gone to the West Mountain.

26:16.640 --> 26:17.700
The West Mountain?

26:18.400 --> 26:20.820
Why did he suddenly
go to the West Mountain?

26:21.200 --> 26:22.720
His villa is there.

26:23.030 --> 26:25.290
Perhaps he went to enjoy the hot springs.

26:28.270 --> 26:29.880
Stop joking.

26:30.680 --> 26:33.070
Lately, the Emperor
has been leaving the palace frequently.

26:33.070 --> 26:33.870
A few days ago,

26:34.200 --> 26:36.720
he rode his carriage
around the city 3 times

26:36.960 --> 26:39.350
and returned
without doing anything at all.

26:39.350 --> 26:40.950
Don't you find that strange?

26:43.270 --> 26:44.960
How many people did the Emperor bring?

26:44.960 --> 26:46.240
He traveled with a light escort,

26:46.240 --> 26:47.270
keeping a very low profile.

26:47.270 --> 26:48.020
It seems

26:48.660 --> 26:50.390
he doesn't want anyone to know.

26:54.720 --> 26:56.590
If that's the case,

26:57.680 --> 27:00.210
why don't we take
this excellent opportunity

27:01.990 --> 27:02.890
and just...

27:04.820 --> 27:05.220
You...

27:07.960 --> 27:10.750
I can have the troops
I've stationed in the suburbs

27:10.750 --> 27:12.010
disguised as bandits.

27:12.350 --> 27:14.590
We can certainly accomplish
this great deed

27:14.590 --> 27:15.990
without anyone knowing.

27:16.110 --> 27:17.170
No, Your Highness!

27:17.510 --> 27:20.270
-Yes, we can't do that, Your Highness!
-There must be something wrong.

27:20.270 --> 27:21.510
We have planned for years

27:21.510 --> 27:23.270
and attempted assassination
more than once,

27:23.270 --> 27:25.270
yet the Emperor has evaded them all.

27:25.830 --> 27:26.550
I don't believe

27:26.550 --> 27:28.680
he's truly as incompetent

27:28.720 --> 27:30.170
as he appears.

27:30.350 --> 27:31.810
I don't believe it either.

27:32.030 --> 27:33.770
-Acting in such haste
-You...

27:34.030 --> 27:36.440
-risks too much.
-Exactly!

27:36.510 --> 27:38.400
Why are you so indecisive?

27:38.590 --> 27:40.990
Opportunities like this don't come twice!

27:41.110 --> 27:41.560
Well...

27:41.560 --> 27:41.960
You...

27:42.030 --> 27:42.430
You...

27:44.440 --> 27:45.010
Sir,

27:45.480 --> 27:48.010
how confident are you
about this bandit plan?

27:48.040 --> 27:48.900
Your Highness!

27:49.790 --> 27:51.440
We've rehearsed for a long time.

27:51.440 --> 27:52.900
I dare not say it's foolproof,

27:52.900 --> 27:53.270
but

27:54.070 --> 27:56.130
our chances of success are very high.

27:57.910 --> 28:00.820
You promised us
all kinds of official positions

28:01.400 --> 28:03.000
in the Ministries of Revenue, Justice,
and Personnel haphazardly,

28:03.000 --> 28:03.790
as if you could actually

28:03.790 --> 28:05.790
control that incompetent emperor.

28:06.750 --> 28:07.210
Indeed.

28:08.400 --> 28:09.530
To serve a wise ruler

28:09.880 --> 28:10.810
with one's life;

28:11.510 --> 28:13.240
to die as a martyr for the country's sake.

28:13.240 --> 28:13.830
Now

28:14.480 --> 28:16.340
the court's capable men are gone.

28:16.510 --> 28:17.430
I almost wish

28:18.200 --> 28:19.510
I could strike the ground with my head

28:19.510 --> 28:20.640
to wake that tyrant.

28:20.650 --> 28:22.650
What do you expect from that tyrant?

28:23.210 --> 28:24.410
But I heard people say

28:25.030 --> 28:26.680
that Prince Duan is skilled
in both civil and military affairs

28:26.680 --> 28:28.880
and could be considered a worthy ruler.

28:29.640 --> 28:31.460
Prince Duan only seeks power.

28:31.550 --> 28:33.440
He has done nothing
for the country or its people.

28:33.440 --> 28:35.240
He cannot be considered worthy.

28:35.310 --> 28:36.640
As the ruler of a nation,

28:36.720 --> 28:38.590
he plunged his people into suffering.

28:38.590 --> 28:39.830
When all is said and done,

28:39.830 --> 28:41.890
the emperor has failed his subjects.

28:43.510 --> 28:45.310
Beautiful women are disasters.

28:45.640 --> 28:46.750
I suppose the tyrant

28:46.750 --> 28:49.510
must have been bewitched
by that demonic consort Yu Wanyin,

28:49.510 --> 28:52.510
-growing ever more muddled and unruly.
-Why me again?

28:53.680 --> 28:54.480
That's right.

28:54.830 --> 28:57.790
As the poem says, "Nights with
the beautiful woman are too short;

28:57.790 --> 29:01.350
from now on, the emperor no longer
attends court in the morning."

29:01.350 --> 29:03.510
Was he a wise ruler

29:04.160 --> 29:06.360
before that demonic consort appeared?

29:06.480 --> 29:08.440
Just say he's incompetent.

29:08.440 --> 29:10.110
Why blame a woman?

29:10.160 --> 29:11.510
Are you defending that demonic consort?

29:11.510 --> 29:12.110
What else?

29:12.480 --> 29:14.550
Do you really believe
that a woman from the harem

29:14.550 --> 29:15.960
can disrupt state affairs?

29:15.960 --> 29:17.200
It's just an excuse.

29:17.510 --> 29:18.550
How is it an excuse?

29:18.550 --> 29:19.440
Everyone says that...

29:19.440 --> 29:20.040
Says what?

29:20.310 --> 29:22.590
That she has a snake-like face
that can peel pears?

29:22.590 --> 29:25.070
You keep calling her
"demonic consort" with such conviction.

29:25.070 --> 29:27.100
Li, have you actually seen her

29:27.240 --> 29:28.640
perform any witchcraft?

29:28.680 --> 29:29.070
Er...

29:29.590 --> 29:30.650
Alright, alright.

29:30.960 --> 29:31.790
-Well said, sis.
-Mr. Li, you care about

29:31.790 --> 29:33.590
-the country and the people.
-You should say more.

29:33.590 --> 29:34.320
I admire you.

29:34.960 --> 29:36.810
Er Lan makes a fair point.

29:37.830 --> 29:38.690
But gentlemen,

29:39.270 --> 29:40.920
aren't we getting off topic?

29:42.000 --> 29:45.400
Who should govern this country
and how it should be governed—

29:45.790 --> 29:46.590
that is what we

29:46.590 --> 29:48.120
should be concerned about.

29:48.350 --> 29:48.950
Am I right?

29:51.480 --> 29:52.280
That's right.

29:53.480 --> 29:55.480
As stated in the letter to all of you,

29:56.030 --> 29:57.310
we must destroy before we can rebuild.

29:57.310 --> 29:58.710
How to break the deadlock

29:58.960 --> 29:59.810
is the key.

30:00.440 --> 30:01.440
In my opinion,

30:01.920 --> 30:03.920
the crux still lies with the people.

30:04.110 --> 30:05.670
Since ancient times,

30:05.670 --> 30:07.550
the capable should be in charge
and the mediocre beneath them.

30:07.550 --> 30:08.840
Yet now it is the mediocre
who are in charge

30:08.840 --> 30:10.400
and the capable who are beneath them.

30:10.400 --> 30:11.680
Without breaking the privileges
of the nobility,

30:11.680 --> 30:13.340
none of this can move forward.

30:13.400 --> 30:14.350
As the saying goes,

30:14.350 --> 30:15.550
"Are kings and nobles

30:15.920 --> 30:17.000
born that way?"

30:17.270 --> 30:17.800
Exactly!

30:18.640 --> 30:19.110
War

30:19.460 --> 30:21.030
does not necessarily destroy a nation,

30:21.030 --> 30:21.550
nor do

30:21.880 --> 30:23.000
famine and disaster.

30:23.000 --> 30:24.160
But there is one thing

30:24.160 --> 30:26.530
that can end a nation's fortune
and make the people lose faith:

30:26.530 --> 30:27.260
when the path

30:27.310 --> 30:29.770
for the poor and talented
to rise is blocked.

30:32.070 --> 30:33.600
You really dare to say that?

30:35.030 --> 30:35.960
Why wouldn't I?

30:37.920 --> 30:39.550
All of us here are commoners.

30:40.160 --> 30:42.160
How much can we truly save Great Xia?

30:42.880 --> 30:44.000
Look up.

30:44.830 --> 30:46.030
There is no clear sky,

30:47.590 --> 30:48.960
only mire and filth.

30:51.160 --> 30:52.830
"Big rats, big rats,

30:54.020 --> 30:55.350
stop eating our grain."

30:56.510 --> 30:57.970
For the sake of the people,

30:58.830 --> 31:00.070
there's nothing we can't do!

31:00.070 --> 31:00.960
Well said!

31:01.750 --> 31:03.550
With your ambition and vision,

31:03.720 --> 31:05.350
there is hope for Great Xia!

31:05.400 --> 31:05.880
Indeed.

31:06.440 --> 31:07.480
But ambition alone,

31:07.480 --> 31:09.000
without the chance to serve in office,

31:09.000 --> 31:11.110
makes saving our nation mere empty talk.

31:11.110 --> 31:12.880
You are indeed like your words.

31:13.680 --> 31:14.720
This drinking session

31:14.720 --> 31:16.120
has been most enjoyable!

31:16.920 --> 31:18.920
But you still haven't told us...

31:21.350 --> 31:22.030
who

31:22.550 --> 31:23.750
you really are.

31:30.070 --> 31:30.800
It's coming!

31:31.830 --> 31:34.230
The climax of this scene
is finally coming!

31:34.790 --> 31:35.990
My humble surname...

31:37.550 --> 31:38.440
is Xiahou.

31:40.640 --> 31:41.840
With such eloquence,

31:41.990 --> 31:43.250
could you be Prince...

31:47.480 --> 31:49.680
I'm afraid you'll be disappointed, Du.

31:51.070 --> 31:52.130
My given name is...

31:53.430 --> 31:54.150
Dan.

31:58.860 --> 31:59.990
As for this lady,

32:01.160 --> 32:03.330
she is the very demonic consort

32:04.070 --> 32:05.530
you were just speaking of,

32:05.960 --> 32:06.790
Yu Wanyin.

32:16.160 --> 32:17.760
Nice to meet you, gentlemen.

32:19.830 --> 32:20.700
I am Wang Zhao.

32:21.160 --> 32:22.620
Greetings, Your Majesty!

32:22.890 --> 32:24.300
-I'm Du Shan.
-I'm Yang Duojie.

32:24.300 --> 32:25.440
-I'm Er Lan.
-Greetings, Your Majesty.

32:25.440 --> 32:26.900
Greetings, Your Majesty.

32:32.510 --> 32:33.690
If you want to kneel, then kneel.

32:33.690 --> 32:35.090
Why pull me down with you?

32:37.780 --> 32:40.350
You expect me to kneel
to this incompetent emperor?

32:40.350 --> 32:41.350
Over my dead body.

32:43.880 --> 32:44.480
Everyone,

32:45.000 --> 32:45.730
please rise.

32:46.000 --> 32:47.860
Please forgive us, Your Majesty.

32:53.030 --> 32:54.090
All you know is that

32:54.640 --> 32:56.240
I am a tyrant, ruling harshly

32:56.550 --> 32:58.010
and preying on the people.

33:00.000 --> 33:01.060
What you do not know

33:02.220 --> 33:03.920
is that over the past ten-plus years,

33:03.920 --> 33:04.900
my power

33:05.350 --> 33:06.880
has long been hollowed out.

33:08.840 --> 33:10.040
Now, half of the court

33:10.880 --> 33:11.680
is controlled

33:12.200 --> 33:13.530
by the Empress Dowager,

33:14.310 --> 33:15.310
and the other half

33:15.830 --> 33:17.430
manipulated by Prince Duan.

33:18.480 --> 33:20.880
They make high-stakes gambles
with the lives

33:20.880 --> 33:23.010
of Great Xia's people again and again.

33:23.160 --> 33:24.490
Though my heart bleeds,

33:25.060 --> 33:26.790
I can only pretend to be a tyrant

33:27.590 --> 33:28.920
to preserve my own life.

33:35.180 --> 33:36.150
Today's meeting

33:38.000 --> 33:38.730
is my attempt

33:39.300 --> 33:41.830
to lay bare my true heart before you,

33:42.440 --> 33:43.500
in the hope that you

33:44.590 --> 33:47.030
might understand my unspoken difficulties.

33:47.030 --> 33:48.480
Your Majesty,
if you truly have such intentions,

33:48.480 --> 33:50.750
why not reform the imperial exam
and recruit talent openly?

33:50.750 --> 33:53.680
Why did you ask us
to meet you in secrecy like thieves?

33:54.510 --> 33:55.970
This way of recruiting men

33:56.590 --> 33:57.110
seems

33:57.960 --> 33:59.560
beneath your royal dignity.

34:01.400 --> 34:03.060
Too many eyes are watching me.

34:04.590 --> 34:06.720
Even the slightest change
to the imperial exam

34:06.720 --> 34:08.800
would face opposition from all sides.

34:08.800 --> 34:11.070
If not for my secret guards
searching everywhere,

34:11.070 --> 34:12.330
your brilliant essays

34:12.510 --> 34:14.370
would never have reached my desk.

34:14.630 --> 34:16.360
I can only contact you in secret

34:17.320 --> 34:18.250
so I can place you

34:18.840 --> 34:20.100
in suitable positions

34:21.110 --> 34:22.969
to realize your grand ambitions.

34:23.960 --> 34:24.620
Therefore,

34:25.760 --> 34:26.960
you should know that

34:27.840 --> 34:29.370
what I promised you just now

34:29.630 --> 34:30.320
was not

34:30.320 --> 34:32.000
empty talk or hollow bait.

34:36.000 --> 34:36.600
Of course,

34:38.190 --> 34:38.710
I know

34:40.000 --> 34:41.659
that my one-sided words alone

34:41.800 --> 34:43.170
cannot, in a single day,

34:43.630 --> 34:45.340
turn your loyal hearts

34:45.920 --> 34:46.630
toward me.

34:47.590 --> 34:48.760
But I must try.

34:49.840 --> 34:50.639
In the future,

34:51.230 --> 34:52.630
when you enter the court,

34:53.030 --> 34:54.060
you will surely be targeted

34:54.060 --> 34:56.230
by the Empress Dowager's
and Prince Duan's factions—

34:56.230 --> 34:56.840
courted,

34:57.510 --> 34:58.170
exploited,

34:59.360 --> 35:00.090
or attacked.

35:00.760 --> 35:01.890
When that day comes,

35:02.800 --> 35:05.760
I only hope you will not forget
the passionate words you spoke

35:05.760 --> 35:07.880
and the lofty aspirations you laid bare

35:07.880 --> 35:09.130
on this boat today.

35:10.960 --> 35:12.360
I hope you will stand tall

35:13.360 --> 35:15.160
and be the backbone of Great Xia.

35:19.360 --> 35:20.590
These are just words

35:20.590 --> 35:22.590
devised to recruit these scholars.

35:23.840 --> 35:25.320
So why do I feel like crying

35:26.880 --> 35:28.070
after hearing it?
